AIM: Develop a Window application to read an XML document containing employee name,code,Basic pay, HRA, DA into a Dataset

PROCEDURE:
Create a windows application using C#.Net

Drag the Datagrid view control and a button into the form.
Create an XML file with the following code and save the file as employee.xml

<?xml version="1.0"?>
<employees>

<employee>
<code> E101 </code>

<name> ASHOK </name>
<basicpay> 12000 </basicpay>
<hra> 1500 </hra>

<da> 8000 </da>
</employee>

<employee>
<code> E102 </code>

<name> BALA </name>
<basicpay> 15000 </basicpay>
<hra> 2000 </hra>

<da> 9000 </da>
</employee>

</employees>

4. Create a windows application using C# .net and design a form with a Datagridview and a button.

Include the namespace at the beginning of the program.
using System.Data.SqlClient;

5.Type the following code under public class Form1

DataSet ds=new DataSet();

Type the following code in the click event of Button1 private void button1_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)

{

ds.ReadXml("d:/employee.xml");
dataGridView1.DataMember = "employee";
dataGridView1.DataSource = ds;
}

6.Run the application.
